				<p>It depends on the requirements of your problems. If you don't mind any boundary condition, you can simply ask the quad to reach from one position to another. But if you have any extra condition, you can implement that when reaching a particular point on the path the quad to be at a certain speed or acceleration. As you see, extra conditions harden the problem a little.</p>
